        <image class="card-image" src="/images/person-1.jpg"></image>
      </view>  
      <view class="card-info">
        <view class='h2'>Calvin Tan</view>
        <view class='p'>Nam condimentum vitae ligula vel ornare. Phasellus at semper turpis. Nunc eu tellus tortor. Etiam at condimentum nisl, vitae sagittis orci. Donec id dignissim nunc.</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>


</view>



